*** '''Father Aereck:''' I believe he is currently living as a hermit in Lumbridge swamp. He has a little shack in the far west of the swamps.
*** '''Father Aereck:''' Exit the graveyard through the south gate to reach the swamp. I'm sure if you told him that I sent you he'd be willing to help.
*** '''Father Aereck:''' My name is Father Aereck by the way. Pleased to meet you.
*** '''Player:''' Likewise.
** '''Father Aereck:''' Take care travelling through the swamps, I have heard they can be quite dangerous.
